            <td class="blob-code">}</td>
            </tr>

        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>While we're here, I'll add a use statement for <code>MinkContext</code> and make it extend that.
I'll explain that in a minute:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="6eb54475e1">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
