	                    </div>
	                    <div class="dsq-comment-body" id="dsq-comment-body-2910176955">
	                        <div class="dsq-comment-header">
	                            <span class="dsq-comment-date">2016-09-22</span>
	                            <span class="dsq-commenter-name">Victor Bocharsky</span>
	                        </div>

	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2910176955" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2910176955" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>One possible cause for this is having a host name without a domain part (.com, .org, etc.), e.g. http://example/ instead of <a href="http://disq.us/url?url=http%3A%2F%2Fexample.com%2F%3An0peNdLersmf0a6Nx5fpJAPFcJk&amp;cuid=1175718" rel="nofollow noopener">http://example.com/</a></p>
	                            </div>
	                        </div>
	                    </div>
	                </li>
	            	                <li class="dsq-comment dsq-clearfix" data-dsq-comment-id="2910166101" id="dsq-comment-2910166101">
	                    <div class="dsq-avatar dsq-tt">
	                        <a href="https://disqus.com/by/disqus_idpJQYpFjJ/">
	                            	                                <img alt="" src="http://a.disquscdn.com/uploads/users/20654/9029/avatar92.jpg?1478365637">
	                            	                        </a>
	                    </div>
	                    <div class="dsq-comment-body" id="dsq-comment-body-2910166101">
	                        <div class="dsq-comment-header">
	                            <span class="dsq-comment-date">2016-09-22</span>
	                            <span class="dsq-commenter-name">Thierno Diop</span>
	                        </div>

	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2910166101" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2910166101" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Thx for your response <br>Session are saved in the folder var/sessions but the problem is that for every request it create one file in the session folder</p>
	                            </div>
	                        </div>
	                    </div>
	                </li>
	            	                <li class="dsq-comment dsq-clearfix" data-dsq-comment-id="2910115308" id="dsq-comment-2910115308">
	                    <div class="dsq-avatar dsq-tt">
	                        <a href="https://disqus.com/by/bocharsky25/">
	                            	                                <img alt="" src="http://a.disquscdn.com/uploads/users/11445/2822/avatar92.jpg?1482506193">
	                            	                        </a>
	                    </div>
	                    <div class="dsq-comment-body" id="dsq-comment-body-2910115308">
	                        <div class="dsq-comment-header">
	                            <span class="dsq-comment-date">2016-09-22</span>
	                            <span class="dsq-commenter-name">Victor Bocharsky</span>
	                        </div>

	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2910115308" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2910115308" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Hey Thierno,</p><p>You should configure session properly - most likely session can't be stored on your server. Where do you store session? If it stores in files - look at <a href="http://disq.us/url?url=http%3A%2F%2Fsymfony.com%2Fdoc%2Fcurrent%2Freference%2Fconfiguration%2Fframework.html%23save-path%3AyypEKvfKr69O1IazqjcW6PwpUYs&amp;cuid=1175718" rel="nofollow noopener">save_path</a> option and ensure you setup permissions for it correctly on the server. Let me know if it helps.</p><p>Cheers!</p>
	                            </div>
	                        </div>
	                    </div>
	                </li>
	            	                <li class="dsq-comment dsq-clearfix" data-dsq-comment-id="2909396729" id="dsq-comment-2909396729">
