	                    </div>
	                    <div class="dsq-comment-body" id="dsq-comment-body-2801862683">
	                        <div class="dsq-comment-header">
	                            <span class="dsq-comment-date">2016-07-25</span>
	                            <span class="dsq-commenter-name">Victor Bocharsky</span>
	                        </div>

	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2801862683" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2801862683" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Hey <a data-dsq-mention="ciudadano82:disqus" href="https://disq.us/url?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdisqus.com%2Fby%2Fciudadano82%2F%3ApH9Ox4YVZZarmt-6A6Jtm8RLWWc&amp;cuid=1175718" rel="nofollow noopener">ciudadano82</a> ,</p><p>You don't have to install GuardBundle for Symfony 3.1 because Guard Component provides with Symfony out of the box since Symfony 2.8, so just start using it without installation! :)</p><p>Check this blog post page for more information: <a href="http://disq.us/url?url=http%3A%2F%2Fsymfony.com%2Fblog%2Fnew-in-symfony-2-8-guard-authentication-component%3AWI8_fM8aYh_cMHWZXRpGjhmmGb8&amp;cuid=1175718" rel="nofollow noopener">http://symfony.com/blog/new-in...</a> .</p><p>Cheers!</p>
