	            	                <li class="dsq-comment dsq-clearfix" data-dsq-comment-id="2754466537" id="dsq-comment-2754466537">
	                    <div class="dsq-avatar dsq-tt">
	                        <a href="https://disqus.com/by/bocharsky25/">
	                            	                                <img alt="" src="http://a.disquscdn.com/uploads/users/11445/2822/avatar92.jpg?1482506193">
	                            	                        </a>
	                    </div>
	                    <div class="dsq-comment-body" id="dsq-comment-body-2754466537">
	                        <div class="dsq-comment-header">
	                            <span class="dsq-comment-date">2016-06-28</span>
	                            <span class="dsq-commenter-name">Victor Bocharsky</span>
	                        </div>

	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2754466537" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2754466537" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Hey, Viral!</p><p>There's the <a href="https://disq.us/url?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fknpuniversity%2FKnpUGuardBundle%3AsjTamumLe51sc8ENdy7K9EEJeHo&amp;cuid=1175718" rel="nofollow noopener">KnpUGuardBundle</a> which you need to install first, because out-of-the-box Guard component available since Symfony ^2.8. only. But keep in mind that some dependencies should be updated to "^2.6". Check composer.json file of KnpUGuardBundle bundle to get more information about versions of dependencies.</p><p>Cheers!</p>
	                            </div>
	                        </div>
	                    </div>
	                </li>
	            	                <li class="dsq-comment dsq-clearfix" data-dsq-comment-id="2754369261" id="dsq-comment-2754369261">
